snippet: Ernests Gulbis, the 13th seed, was eliminated from the Monte Carlo Masters in the first round, losing to Andreas Haider-Maurer, 6-1, 6-0.
abstract: Andreas Haider-Maurer defeats Ernests Gulbis in first round of the Monte Carlo Masters tennis tournament.
